            <paragraph align="center">○以<index num="1094024_0" ref="M_0003529" sort="K" type="이름">禹伏龍</index>爲內贍直長。 <index num="1094025_0" ref="M_0003529" sort="K" type="이름">伏龍</index>以薦補參奉, <index num="1094026_0" ref="M_0000646" sort="K" type="이름">李珥</index>薦其踐履篤實、學行著聞, 請依<index num="1094027_0" ref="M_0000876" sort="K" type="이름">鄭逑</index>例, 陞六品職, 上只許陞敍, 故有除。</paragraph>
