            <paragraph align="center">○朔乙酉/帝遣翰林院編修<index num="1094113_0" ref="M_0034340" sort="A" sort2="명" type="이름">黃洪憲</index>、兵科右給事中<index num="1094114_0" ref="M_0033002" sort="A" sort2="명" type="이름">王敬民</index>, 來頒皇嗣誕生詔。 以<index num="1094115_0" ref="M_0000646" sort="K" type="이름">李珥</index>爲遠接使, <index num="1094116_0" ref="M_0000646" sort="K" type="이름">珥</index>辟<index num="1094117_0" ref="M_0060561" sort="K" type="이름">許篈</index>、<index num="1094118_0" ref="M_0001045" sort="K" type="이름">高敬命</index>、<index num="1094119_0" ref="M_0035177" sort="K" type="이름">金瞻</index>爲從事官, 禮曹判書<index num="1094120_0" ref="M_0005860" sort="K" type="이름">鄭惟吉</index>爲館伴。</paragraph>
